{
  "stem": "15694.11",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think they were Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, we are-- they were the low and we were the lowest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were searching us because they had a good result yesterday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were thinking maybe they'll find something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And as they were searching I could see my neighbor fidgeting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he had, in his hand-- I don't know if he had more than that-- sort of a tin of something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was dented badly in the middle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Instead of him handing it to-- out of fear-- to the others, I grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had my trousers in my boots, let it down inside my trousers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it sort of wrapped itself around my ankles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And sort of, for the first gloves, it wouldn't be seen, like knickerbockers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he searched everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then one came to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And not he-- a number-- a number of them, sort of they did it fast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And just in case, not wanting their comrades to find more than they did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They came to me, and I said, I have nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "All I have is-- and I pull it out of my pocket, the onion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it was, by the time-- it was then blood soaked, by that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I lifted him-- in order for his glances to look up and not down, I lifted it over his head as he was searching my pockets already, before he went down any further.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And a drop of blood fell on his face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he cursed me and pushed me away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I kept my bloody onion, or half onion, by that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And as I went on to the train, the wagon-- the-- the hospital train was open.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
